            "value": "a full path in windows \"C:\\somewhere\\somefile.php\" fails the security check, and cannot be used to load files using the Zend_loader (cause of the \":\" character)\n\nmoreover, in windows 64bit, if files are located under the Program Files directory - which is called \"Program files (86)\" in the 64bit version - it fails as well (cause of the \"(\" character)"
